I want to write a different way of `getTopicsBitmap` with different implementations in eth_receipts.go.
Now the method has following function: 

```go
// The Topic list restricts matches to particular event topics. Each event has a list
// of topics. Topics matches a prefix of that list. An empty element slice matches any
// topic. Non-empty elements represent an alternative that matches any of the
// contained topics.
//
// Examples:
// {} or nil          matches any topic list
// {{A}}              matches topic A in first position
// {{}, {B}}          matches any topic in first position AND B in second position
// {{A}, {B}}         matches topic A in first position AND B in second position
// {{A, B}, {C, D}}   matches topic (A OR B) in first position AND (C OR D) in second position
```

Here is my implementation: 

```go
// The Topic list restricts matches to particular event topics. Each event has a list
// of topics. Topics matches a prefix of that list. An empty element slice matches any
// topic. Non-empty elements represent an alternative that matches any of the
// contained topics.
//
// Examples:
// {} or nil          matches nothing
// {{A}}              matches topic A in first position
// {{}, {B}}          matches nothing OR B in first position
// {{A}, {B}}         matches topic A in first position OR B in first position
// {{A, B}, {C, D}}   matches topic (A AND B) in first & second positions OR (C AND D) in first & second positions.
```

Anyone come up with a good method name? Of course I won't change the original method but adding a new method implementation instead.
